61
00:10:35,901 --> 00:10:37,596
What's keeping her?

62
00:10:39,538 --> 00:10:41,904
I don't know.

63
00:10:43,142 --> 00:10:44,473
Well whatever.

64
00:10:44,977 --> 00:10:47,445
