65
00:10:47,747 --> 00:10:48,941
Thanks.

66
00:12:52,938 --> 00:12:53,996
Ms. Kawaguchi?

67
00:13:53,532 --> 00:13:54,692
Ms. Sawada?

68
00:13:56,135 --> 00:13:58,729
Ms. Kawaguchi?

69
