249
00:31:08,466 --> 00:31:10,127
Our newest member.

250
00:31:10,235 --> 00:31:10,997
Watch me, okay?

251
00:31:16,040 --> 00:31:17,598
Count me out.

252
00:31:21,846 --> 00:31:27,716
